{"tid":2140850,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【連登好似冇人講】推介幾個日本YouTube動畫漫畫Channel","createTime":"2020-08-05T09:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T12:43:58.000Z","uid":90433,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"98fd9069ca21df68c93943ab529500e09cd3d5eb","tid":2140850,"uid":90433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:16:20.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇巴絲有睇開Youtube動畫／Youtube漫畫動畫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢類Channel通常都係幾分鐘到十分鐘嘅片為主，雖然唔似一般電視動畫咁有成個世界觀故事線，但就有好多種唔同嘅題材，好似小知識、心理學、都市傳說之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話就話冇乜主線，不過有睇開嘅話，會知道每個Channel隱隱約約有啲角色設定嘅，下面拋吓波講幾個自己有追開嘅Channel先，有啲得日文，有啲有出埋中/英文版（附埋link畀大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>【秘密結社YARUMINATI・秘密結社ヤルミナティー】</strong><br />\nYoutube：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/xnbtf194/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fxnbtf194%2Fvideos&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeamWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=5550d71d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/xnbtf194/videos</a><br />\nChannel個名係改編自光明會Illuminati，角色有團長長頸鹿、狂暴豬TABOO同難得嘅正常人後輩HACK<br />\n以各地都市傳說、鬼談做主題，基本上都一集完，暫時好似得日文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比較多人識嘅<strong>「如月車站」</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IHOez8fb7kA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIHOez8fb7kA&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeamWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=d07f7de4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IHOez8fb7kA</a>"},{"pid":"620540ee726e994607c601568dadc74f6633c271","tid":2140850,"uid":90433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:18:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>【反抗吧！企鵝・テイコウペンギン】</strong><br />\nYoutube：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hreHfKyLqz8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhreHfKyLqz8&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeamWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=4a3739b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hreHfKyLqz8</a><br />\n打工仔睇應該會有好大共鳴感，佢係講企鵝同熊貓入咗去間黑心企業做，然後被無良上司逼咗去拍Youtuber，之後就衍生出好多社畜日常故事<span class=\"medium\">（身在日本做緊社畜表示好有同感&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n主題嚟講，有講黑心企業點樣剝削員工嘅社畜劇場，亦有企鵝熊貓去做其他職業嘅社畜體驗，有時仲有啲小知識、神秘詭異嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如企鵝同熊貓做咗IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GWpKT7R37_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGWpKT7R37_s&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeamWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=86d1d2cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GWpKT7R37_s</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個講暗網<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r9H_h2BT_l4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr9H_h2BT_l4&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeamWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=800e4597\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r9H_h2BT_l4</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有做炒狗嘅下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7gk2JptJSPo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7gk2JptJSPo&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeamWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=8e263eee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7gk2JptJSPo</a><br />\n<br />\n日文版Youtube：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUTgXNqRBqR33D5q10DfQXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCUTgXNqRBqR33D5q10DfQXw&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeamWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=b9bcdbbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUTgXNqRBqR33D5q10DfQXw</a>"},{"pid":"f747670652e57d8d75fd903b8790f3e3cba6f780","tid":2140850,"uid":90433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:19:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>【Comic Panda・コミックパンダ】</strong><br />\nYoutube：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mvivl4VTW1c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F